00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:31.719
the dagger used for murder

00:01:32.040 --> 00:01:33.319
must be carefully guarded.

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:36.439
It must absolutely not fall into
the hands of others.

00:01:48.439 --> 00:01:49.799
Yan's reminder is timely.

00:01:50.239 --> 00:01:51.599
If we succeed,

00:01:52.319 --> 00:01:54.879
I will happily marry
into the Prince Duan's Residence.

00:01:55.599 --> 00:01:56.760
If we fail,

00:01:57.130 --> 00:01:59.719
I shall use my own fresh blood
to make a sacrifice to this blade.

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:03.280
How could I bear to use you
as a sacrifice?

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:06.290
Though I do not possess
the overwhelming power of Pei Yu,

00:02:06.519 --> 00:02:07.760
as long as I live for a day,

00:02:08.439 --> 00:02:09.919
I will protect you completely.

